Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At long last, I understand \Nwhere babies come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.46,0:00:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear you've finally\Ntaken my explanation to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if we're to have a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us embark upon this journey together...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dead meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-a ghost...?!
