Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokorogoroshi yarisugosu owaranai \Nzange to yuuutsu no yoru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokorogoroshi yarisugosu owaranai \Nzange to yuuutsu no yoru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzen na jibun ga dokonimo inai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saitei na jibun shika mitsukaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... you're a thief, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:27.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3: Peter Grill and \NRelationships with Elves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put up a fight, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mere! There's nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you cretin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything would be fine \Nif you had stayed asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good ol' Peter sure is rowdy tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He drinkin' in his room or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, knock-knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you fussin' around \Nin the dark for...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A girl...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release me, you imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this whole thing to the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tim Robinson withdraws coolly."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, this isn't what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Tim-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tim-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheatin' on her, eh?\NTim-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tim-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dude's got balls of steel...\NTim-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dude's got balls of steel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I'll have to do \Nthis the old-fashioned way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Vegan Eldoriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have traveled here as the designated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,goodwill ambassador from the land of my brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demi-human...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Female...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've got a VERY bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she's got the same idea\Nas those crazy Ogre sisters...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the reason I've traveled here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to acquire the \Nnectar of your nethers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point I'm afraid to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why ME, exactly...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good question, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would us members of the proud Elven race
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,require the seed of an inferior Human such as yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer, of course, is none other than to save\Nour beloved village from total annihilation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A humiliating subject though it may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our nation has continually failed to yield sufficient\Nresults at the Grand Fighting Tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an event that celebrates combat prowess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the object of ridicule amongst neighboring\Ncountries who terrorize us with acts of aggression,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and our international reputation \Nis slowly deteriorating...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite taking various countermeasures,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elves are a physically weak species.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,History proves that we aren't \Nsuited for military conquest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therein lies MY role!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Council has chosen to adopt a\Nresolution stating that we shall aim
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to obtain an optimal genetic\Nspecimen from an outside source!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as the designated goodwill ambassador,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been tasked with the responsibility\Nof bringing back your juices!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with that being said, Peter Grill...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You are welcome to play with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As much as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are these demi-human types completely\Nincapable of considering MY point of view?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is breeding the only thing they care about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, to be honest with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't necessarily mind being \Napproached by cute girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not! I mean, who would?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I appreciate the offer, \NI must respectfully decline!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying a plebeian Human\Nlike you would let the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to mate with a member of the\Nnoble Elven race such as I go to waste?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The superiority complex \Nis strong with this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty typical comin' from an Elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall squeeze every \Nlast drop out of you by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening! Just take a look for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does my sublime body not arouse\Nthat ugly meatstick of yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have an erection?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as my heart belongs to another,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the blood in my veins shall refrain\Nfrom flowing to my spongy tissues!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impotent moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to fulfill my\Nduties as an ambassador now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've left me no choice but \Nto utilize my secret weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with this light...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell'd you do to my crotch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's far too late for \Napologies, you imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The curse I placed upon you is a powerful\Ntype of forbidden sorcery
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's been carefully sealed\Naway in my homeland for generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-forbidden sorcery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to share with you a prediction:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow night,\Nyou shall appear before me and drop to your knees,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pleading for mercy in a pitiful voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please, I'll do anything for \Nyou to sample my man goo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, please let me bang you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was oddly specific, don't you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we meet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fare thee well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the light died out... \NMy junk looks normal, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, I've never heard of a spell used\Nto mess with a man's dangly bits...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's bluffing, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's time to get \Nready for today's hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm itchin' for some action!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the villagers,\Nthe creature supposedly emerges around dusk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Luvellia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nighttime is nearly upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be in grave danger should the sun set\Nbefore we're able to locate the creature's lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we ought to wait for the\Ncombat unit to arrive and try again
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lady Luvellia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible news!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lady Luvellia...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she should've already left for the hot\Nsprings area as part of the vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm headed out now, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just received word from our messenger that\Nshe's been ambushed by the creature...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on our intel, this is \Nthe creature who attacked her:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Worm Goblin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it wreaks havoc across the village at sunset,\Ndevouring the men and defiling the women!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accursed demon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Luvellia, it's too risky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall act as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escape while the creature is distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot in good conscience surrender now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, you fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Luvellia...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajimari wa tada no koigokoro
